title: Google Cloud for India
description: This talk will help you understand overall landscape of Google Cloud Platform (GCP). Here, we will take a brief look at some of the commonly used features and most relevant for Indian developers.

title: Scale your Web Application on Compute Engine
description: A session with a demo explaining the multi-tier web app on Compute Engine. It will cover the information related to: IAAS Market stats, choosing right compute services, Multi-tier application with their role, Load Testing, Demo on autoscaling, etc.

title: Migrating to TypeScript at scale
description: Big changes at big organizations are hard to manage and tricky to maintain, this talk is to tell you how I brought TypeScript to Naukri.

title: Benefits of CTF and Bug Bounty
description: A close look of what is the community and how it works for the welfare of the people in and around the globe. What are the various steps/options to get into these communities and enjoy the amazing learning opportunities.

title: Kotlin for Android - Best Practices & Extensions
description: Kotlin for Android development (official language) brings in a lot of power to developers. This session covers Kotlin programming best practices, Reactive Extensions & Android KTX extensions to make your Android code more efficient, scalable & readable.

title: Firebase for Web
description: This session will focus on the concepts of Firebase and how it can be used for web. It will be a workshop/codelab on How to make a web app using Firebase with Vanila JavaScript.

title: #IamRemarkable Workshop
description: #IamRemarkable is a Google initiative empowering women and underrepresented groups to celebrate their achievements in the workplace and beyond having goals to 1) Improve the self promotion motivation and skills of women and underrepresented groups and 2) Challenge the social perception around self promotion.

title: Women Oriented Session
description: Some mind-blowing stuffs have been planned for our awesome women attendees with lots of exposure.

title: Welcome Keynote
description: Official start of the conference. Greetings from the organizers. This session will be an lightening session about the agenda and other things related to DevFest Punjab. We are very much excited to welcome you people.

title: Closing Keynote
description: Things never finish well without a proper thank you note, or you can say, conclusion is must after day long festival. Make sure you won't miss ending notes & Success Stories from Community.
